OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening and night with outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain spreading from the west. Rain
OL,8,Fpatchy across the south but heavy
OL,9,Facross Argyll. Strong southwesterly
OL,10,Fwinds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FRain, occasionally heavy,
OL,13,Fwill spread southeast across all parts
OL,14,Fin the morning. Then drier with a few
OL,15,Fshowers following on in the afternoon.
OL,16,FWindy at first.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
